# agents.conf — the agent roster. Bootstrap generates the real one at repo root
# (agents.conf, git-ignored) from your answers. This is just a reference.
#
# Columns (whitespace-separated):
#   tmux_key   AgentName   working_dir
#
#   tmux_key    = short tmux session name (first letter(s), lowercase). Must be unique.
#   AgentName   = full name (shown in Remote Control, passed to --name).
#   working_dir = path relative to VAULT_PATH. "." = vault root = the ORCHESTRATOR.
#
# Exactly one agent must have working_dir "." — that's your orchestrator.

# key   name        dir
g       Gamma       .
f       Finance     Finance
h       Health      Health
t       Tasks       Tasks
j       Journal     Journal
